sentences: Church Tongue is an American metalcore band that originated in 2015 in Indianapolis, Indiana.
Church Tongue, originally Conquerors, started in 2015.
In 2016, the band signed to Blood and Ink Records.
On October 21, 2016, the band released their debut album, Heart Failure via Blood & Ink.
Alongside the album, the band released a music video for "Acid Jesus" on March 10, 2017.
